&lt;Rapidtech Systems Inc> said itacquired all rights to the patent for the "pocket modem", whicheliminates the need for stand-alone modems that are attachedbetween telephones and computer terminals, as well as modemsbuilt into computers.    Rapidtech said the patent includes all rights to licenseand build the modems, as well as a patent application for anoptical isolator.    The company did not disclose a price for the rights. Reuter&#3;